title: Honey-Can-Do 2-Tier Wood Shoe Rack Espresso SHO-08412 Brown
features: Declutters entryways by housing up to 8 pairs of shoes
Rustic gray wooden finish imbues a natural aesthetic
Slim profile tucks neatly into a hallway or closet
Slatted shelves for better air circulation and fresher footwear
Easy to assemble; no tools needed
description: Since they go almost everywhere with you, your favorite shoes deserve a place of honor. This two-tier wooden shoe rack keeps up to 8 pairs of your most beloved kicks close at hand. The shelves' wooden slats allow air to circulate underneath, so damp soles don't stay that way. This wooden shoe rack is not only sturdy, but it's also attractive, yet unassuming, in an espresso-toned wood.
